  "description": "A ***critical essay*** is an [essay](../../../terms/essay.md) that applies an analytical framework to a text, event, or cultural phenomenon. The writer does not merely describe or summarize the subject but interprets it — reading it through a lens that reveals something not visible on the surface.",
